{
  "title": "MeshBuilder",
  "description": "CPU mesh-geometry builders, grouped as a namespace so the public API carries no loose `build*` functions. Named `MeshBuilder` (not `Geometry`) to avoid clashing with the rendering `Geometry` class. The underlying functions stay module exports for internal use; only this facade is in the public barrel.",
